227
00:19:09,550 --> 00:19:13,850
Thế nên
em chịu đựng anh lâu vậy.

228
00:19:13,900 --> 00:19:15,000
Anh nói đúng.

229
00:19:16,300 --> 00:19:18,450
– Vậy…
– Vậy…

230
00:19:18,500 --> 00:19:19,900
<i>Thế nào?</i>

231
00:19:20,900 --> 00:19:24,950
